headline: Workday to Announce Fiscal 2026 Second Quarter Financial Results on August 21, 2025
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people, money, and agents, plans to announce its fiscal 2026 second quarter financial results after market close on Thursday, August 21, 2025. The company will host a conference call at 1:30 p.m. Pacific Time / 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time to review its financial results and business outlook.

headline: Workday to Hold Annual Financial Analyst Day on September 16, 2025
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people, money, and agents, today announced that it will host its financial analyst day on Tuesday, September 16, 2025 in San Francisco at 2:00 p.m. Pacific Time / 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time. The event will take place during Workday Rising, the company's annual flagship conference for finance, HR, and IT professionals.
